Header include order:
 - Alphabetize within subgroups
 - Group 1
   - sys/types.h (as needed)
   - kernel, sys (e.g. linux/if.h, sys/stat.h)
   - networking headers
 - Group 2
   - headers directly in /usr/include (e.g. string.h, unistd.h, stdint.h)
 - Group 3
   - C++ headers
   - Boost headers
 - Group 4
   - Headers for external libraries (e.g. OpenSSL), grouped by library
